ng a vast swath of North America with Alaska in the northwest and Hawaii extending the nation’s presence into the Pacific Ocean. Major Atlantic Coast cities are New York a global finance and culture center and capital Washington DC. Midwestern metropolis Chicago is known for influential architecture and on the west coast Los Angeles'''' Hollywood is famed for filmmaking.''', '1', '9147420', '213000000', '65', '20', '45', '341711', '954806', '0.59', '36', '38', '83', '99', '12', '21', 'Northern America', 'https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/United_States', 'https://www.britannica.com/place/United-States', 'http://www.americanbible.org/', 'https://unitedbiblesocieties.org/locations/american-bible-society/', 'https://www.cia.gov/the-world-factbook/countries/united-states/', 'https://images.bible.cloud/maps/summary/US-summary.pdf', NULL, 'https://www.nationsonline.org/oneworld/united_states.htm', 'https://curlie.org/Regional/North_America/United_States', 'https://operationworld.org/locations/united-states-of-america', NULL, 'https://joshuaproject.net/countries/US', 'https://prayercast.com/usa.html', 'https://player.vimeo.com/video/23173134', 'http://www.prayercast.com/downloads/direct_download.php?file=USA_dload_hi.mov', 'The World Messianic Bible is a Public Domain translation of the Holy Bible into modern English as spoken among Messianic Jews. It has also been called the World English Bible: Messianic Edition and the Hebrew Names Version.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
