re established in 1999. The latter was suspended until May 2007 due to wrangling over the peace process but devolution was fully completed in March 2010.', 'The United Kingdom made up of England Scotland Wales and Northern Ireland is an island nation in northwestern Europe. England – birthplace of Shakespeare and The Beatles – is home to the capital London a globally influential centre of finance and culture. England is also site of Neolithic Stonehenge Bath’s Roman spa and centuries-old universities at Oxford and Cambridge.', '1', '241930', '33200000', '59.3', '8.9', '50', '133094', '260650', '0.53', '281', '40', '83', '99', '10', '154', 'Northern Europe', 'https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/United_Kingdom', 'https://www.britannica.com/place/United-Kingdom', 'https://www.biblesociety.org.uk/', 'https://unitedbiblesocieties.org/locations/british-and-foreign-bible-society/', 'https://www.cia.gov/the-world-factbook/countries/united-kingdom/', 'https://images.bible.cloud/maps/summary/UK-summary.pdf', 'https://hdr.undp.org/data-center/specific-country-data#/countries/USA', 'https://www.nationsonline.org/oneworld/united_kingdom.htm', 'https://curlie.org/Regional/Europe/United_Kingdom', 'https://operationworld.org/locations/united-kingdom-of-gb-ni', 'https://www.state.gov/countries-areas/united-kingdom/', 'https://joshuaproject.net/countries/GB', 'https://prayercast.com/england.html', 'https://player.vimeo.com/video/37676816', 'http://www.prayercast.com/downloads/direct_download.php?file=England_dload_hi.mov', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
