devolution was fully completed in March 2010.', 'The United Kingdom made up of England Scotland Wales and Northern Ireland is an island nation in northwestern Europe. England – birthplace of Shakespeare and The Beatles – is home to the capital London a globally influential centre of finance and culture. England is also site of Neolithic Stonehenge Bath’s Roman spa and centuries-old universities at Oxford and Cambridge.', '1', '241930', '33200000', '59.3', '8.9', '50', '133094', '260650', '0.53', '281', '40', '83', '99', '10', '154', 'Northern Europe', 'https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/United_Kingdom', 'https://www.britannica.com/place/United-Kingdom', 'https://www.biblesociety.org.uk/', 'https://unitedbiblesocieties.org/locations/british-and-foreign-bible-society/', 'https://www.cia.gov/the-world-factbook/countries/united-kingdom/', 'https://images.bible.cloud/maps/summary/UK-summary.pdf', 'https://hdr.undp.org/data-center/specific-country-data#/countries/USA', 'https://www.nationsonline.org/oneworld/united_kingdom.htm', 'https://curlie.org/Regional/Europe/United_Kingdom', 'https://operationworld.org/locations/united-kingdom-of-gb-ni', 'https://www.state.gov/countries-areas/united-kingdom/', 'https://joshuaproject.net/countries/GB', 'https://prayercast.com/england.html', 'https://player.vimeo.com/video/37676816', 'http://www.prayercast.com/downloads/direct_download.php?file=England_dload_hi.mov', 'Wycliffe’s Bible with Modern Spelling (Enhanced) is a composite of my Wycliffe’s Bible, a modern-spelling version of the 14th century Middle English translation, consisting of Wycliffe’s Old Testament and Wycliffe’s New Testament, and my modern-spelling version of Wycliffe’s Apocrypha. These books contain literally tens of thousands of rewritten verses, presented in parentheses “( ) “, to provide help in comprehending the 14th century Middle English vocabulary and grammar. Wycliffe’s Apocrypha also includes the books of the Apocrypha from the 1st edition of the King James Version of the Bible.', '[1 items in bible_pod.csv]', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
